name: The Cactilogue
description:
HAIII CUTIE, THANKS FOR STOPPING BY <3  

This is just a peaceful little relaxing experience <3 You can't get a game over but CAN YOU PASS THE SKILL CHECKS?

Use your hands to buy new pots  [Left Click]  

Use the shovel to plant new cacti [Left Click and Select from the Menu]  

<3 <3 <3  

I made all the art but I DID NOT make the music, just the SFX :3
